= README for feram-X.YY.ZZ/src/03example-BaTiO3-bulk-phase-transition/24x24x24-20000-200000/
Heating-up and cooling-down simulations of BaTiO3.
== References
 * A set of parameters for effective Hamiltonian described in this article is used. GPa = -5.0.
   W. Zhong, D. Vanderbilt, and K. M. Rabe: "First-principles theory of ferroelectric
   phase transitions for perovskites: The case of BaTiO3", Phys. Rev. B, vol.52,
   pp.6301-6312 (1995) doi:10.1103/PhysRevB.52.6301.

